                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Hagerstown</placeName>\n                <date>April 16/63</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. I Leeser</addressee>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I take the liberty to address<lb/> to you these few lines to inform\n                in regard to<lb/> the proceedings of a certain gentleman named<lb/> “<persName>Rabbi\n                    Holstein</persName>” whom you gave a good<lb/>\n                <sic>reccomendation</sic> as a man who would &amp; could<lb/> with integrity fill\n                the office of a Schoet &amp;<lb/> Hassan, but I am sorry to say you were\n                greatly<lb/> mistaken in your man as you will hear from<lb/> the following facts\n                which I hope you will place<lb/> in a <sic>conspicous</sic> part of your much\n                valuable<lb/> Paper, the “Occident” for it is a disgrace to the<lb/> Jewish name.\n                    <persName>Mr Holstein</persName> came here last<lb/>\n                <date>January</date> with his family with letters of<lb/>\n                <sic>reccomendation</sic> from <persName>Rev Dr Raphel</persName> of\n                    <placeName>New<lb/> York</placeName> &amp; <persName>Rev I. Leeser</persName> of\n                    <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName> as a<lb/> man capable to instruct the\n                children of<lb/> this town in various forms &amp; rites of the<lb/> Jewish Religion\n                &amp; also to butcher for the<lb/> Jewish families of this town so that could<lb/>\n                live like true Israelites, but the disgraced his<lb/> office in the following\n                manner. First he<lb/> persuaded a certain man here a butcher &amp; a<lb/>\n                <persName>Jehuda</persName> to leave his wife &amp; children, &amp; at last<lb/> had\n                so much power over this man that he</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3nk36r3p/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
