                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3nk36r3p/manifest/annotation/p3",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>and send me the “Occident” in which you will<lb/> place it I remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Your obedient Serv't</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Jacob J. Greenewald</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Son of <persName>Mr Greeenewald</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">of the firm <persName>Greenewald &amp;<lb/>Kohlberg</persName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                <placeName>No 110 N. Third</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Please excuse</p>\n            <p>mistakes &amp; bad writing</p>\n            <p>N. B. Give the above to <persName>Dr Wise</persName> of\n                        <placeName><sic>Cincinatti</sic></placeName><lb/> so that he can place in\n                public print<lb/> Yours <persName role=\"author\">JJG</persName>.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3nk36r3p/canvas/p3"
